UID:xhy340DcMnEhMc2kY6JNq
SUMMARY:Bleeding Hearts Club: Land and Community Tending at Frink Park
DTSTAMP:20260205T082837Z
DTSTART:20260214T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Frink Park. \\nBleeding
	 Hearts Club: You’re invited to a community land gathering rooted in slown
	ess\\\, care\\\, and shared responsibility.\\nTogether\\\, we’ll tend the 
	land through ivy cut-and-roll\\\, blackberry clearing\\\, composting\\\, a
	nd observation — guided by attention\\\, not urgency.\\nThese gatherings a
	re a return to land\\\, to care\\\, and to being in right relationship.\\n
	Come Listen to Slow Jams\\\, sink your hands in the soil\\\, gaze at your 
	loves through dappled light\\\, and eat snacks! \\n🖤 Write Love Notes for 
	the Land and Leave Beauty Behind. \\nCome to work. Come to observe. Come t
	o rest.\\nAll forms of participation are welcome. \\nTools\\\, gloves\\\, 
